Description: Tropicana Refreshers Fruit Punch juice drink, previously called Caribbean Sunset - is made with real fruit juice, no artificial sweeteners, and has 90 calories per 8 fl oz serving. Savor the combination of unique flavors with the sweetness of pineapple, cherry, orange and apple. Stock up on Tropicana Refreshers juice drinks and enjoy the refreshingly delicious burst of flavor in every bottle.
